* Symbol Table Type Byte Definitions

* The Type Byte Of An Entry In The Symbol Table Contains The
*    Following Information:

*  Bits 0-2; Data Type - Byte,Integer,Real,Boolean,String,Record
*  Bits 3-4; Shape - Simple,One Dim,Two Dim,Three Dim
*  Bits 5-7; Definition - Undefined,Type Definition,Variable,
*                         Parameter,User Function

* Mask Values

S.DEFM equ $E0 Definition mask
S.SHPM equ $18 Shape mask
S.TYPM equ $07 Type mask

* Least Significant Bit Of Field Values

S.DEF1 equ $20 Definition lsb
S.SHP1 equ $08 Shape lsb
S.TYP1 equ $01 Type lsb

